From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Victor Momplet <mompletvictor@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Jul 2026 18:33:09 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] feat: Porcelain light style + re-skinned launcher icon

Adds a second light token set (cool iOS-style grouped background, AA blue
accent, red-to-green data ramps) behind a new Appearance sub-preference
'Light style: Paper / Porcelain'. The AppearanceMode enum is untouched, so
onboarding and SYSTEM composition keep working; Palette.isLight now treats
any non-dark set as light. Launcher vectors re-skinned to the fork's blue
tile + white loop mark (Navy alias untouched).
---
